playstore_details.title: Smart Scale
playstore_details.description:
A simple and efficient body tracking scale app for your family. 

* Smart Scale could support 8 users at the same time
* Smart Scale could track the weight, body fat %, body water %, muscle %, bone mass, daily caloric intake, visceral fat, and physique rating, etc.
* Smart Scale support to input the weight manually.
* Smart Scale could interact with the Bluetooth4.0 weight scale, fat scale and kids scale.
* Smart Scale could track records by day and month. 
* Smart Scale introduce some great tools and services to keep you in healthy.
* Smart Scale could show the reference normal body data. 
* Smart Scale could share your body measurement result and records to your friends by SNS.

Available on Android 4.3 or above system.
